Hello. This is my mod called EFLC Vehicle Menu.
Press F5 to open up the menu, choose a vehicle and then press enter to spawn it. You will also automatically warp into the vehicle as the driver. You can go down to Quit or press F5 to close the menu.

You can spawn all EFLC cars, bikes, helicopters and boats.

Note: This mod also have vehicle godmode.



Credits:
tjackiseN/r4pp3


Installation:
Put the files in your Grand Theft Auto IV folder.


Video: Go to youtube and search for 'tjackisen eflc vehicle menu'
